---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 96
  - Title: Lankavatara Sutra
    Location: VII
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Cosmic Dream
  - Combat-Action=Work, Action and Society=On ‘Karma’ and ‘Karma Yoga’
---
All things are to be regarded as forms seen in a vision and a dream, empty of
substance, un born and without self-nature, ... (existing) only by reason of
a complicated network of causation which owes its rise to discrimination and
attachment and which eventuates in the rise of the mind-system and its
belongings and evolvements.
